column2: SELECT search_id AS up_id, ra AS up_ra, dec AS up_dec FROM MyDB.IRAS_ULIRG_pos CREATE TABLE #tmp (up_id int, objid bigint) INSERT INTO #tmp EXEC spGetNeighbors # INSERT INTO MyDB.tmp1# SELECT MIN (tmp.up_id) AS up_id, tmp.objid AS objid FROM #tmp tmp INNER JOIN DR1#.PhotoPrimary po ON po.objid = tmp.objid LEFT OUTER JOIN DR1#.Photoz pz ON pz.objid = tmp.objid LEFT OUTER JOIN DR1#.SpecObj sp ON sp.bestobjid = tmp.objid LEFT OUTER JOIN DR1#.TwoMassXSC tm ON tm.objid = tmp.objid LEFT OUTER JOIN DR1#.FIRST ft ON ft.objid = tmp.objid GROUP BY tmp.objid ORDER BY up_id, objid
